0 caf\\u00e9 de concentr\\u00e9 de tomate<\\/span><\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf7e<\\/span>\\n<span><strong><\\/strong> 1 c. \\u00e0 soupe d\\u2019huile d\\u2019olive<\\/span><\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf57<\\/span>\\n<span><strong><\\/strong> 300 ml de bouillon de poulet<\\/span><\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83d\\udca7<\\/span>\\n<span><strong><\\/strong> 400 ml d\\u2019eau (pour les p\\u00e2tes)<\\/span><\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf7e<\\/span>\\n<span><strong><\\/strong> 1 \\u00e0 1,5 c. \\u00e0 caf\\u00e9 de vinaigre balsamique<\\/span><\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf6f<\\/span>\\n<span><strong><\\/strong> \\u00bd c. \\u00e0 caf\\u00e9 de sucre<\\/span><\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83c\\udf5d<\\/span>\\n<span><strong><\\/strong> 250 g de spaghetti<\\/span><\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 12px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 1.1em;\\\">\\n            <span style=\\\"font-size: 1.2em;\\\">\\ud83e\\uddc0<\\/span>\\n<span><strong><\\/strong> 1 c. \\u00e0 soupe de parmesan r\\u00e2p\\u00e9 pour servir<\\/span><\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<div style=\\\"height: 10px; background: #f1f2f6; margin: 20px -35px; border-top: 1px solid #dfe6e9; border-bottom: 1px solid #dfe6e9;\\\"><\\/div>\\n<h3 style=\\\"margin: 25px 0; font-size: 1.5em; color: #2d3436; border-bottom: 2px solid #ffde59; padding-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block;\\\">\\ud83d\\udc68\\u200d\\ud83c\\udf73 Pr\\u00e9paration<\\/h3>\\n<ol id=\\\"mpprecipe-instructions-list\\\" style=\\\"padding-left: 25px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.8; color: #2d3436;\\\">\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">Dans une grande po\\u00eale, faire chauffer l\\u2019huile d\\u2019olive et faire revenir l\\u2019oignon et l\\u2019ail jusqu\\u2019\\u00e0 ce qu\\u2019ils deviennent fondants.<\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">Ajouter le paprika, l\\u2019origan et les flocons de piment, puis m\\u00e9langer.<\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">Mixer le Boursin avec les poivrons grill\\u00e9s, le concentr\\u00e9 de tomate, le vinaigre balsamique et le bouillon jusqu\\u2019\\u00e0 obtenir une sauce lisse.<\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">Verser dans la po\\u00eale, ajouter les spaghettis crus directement dans la sauce, puis ajouter l\\u2019eau sur les p\\u00e2tes.<\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">Couvrir et laisser mijoter une dizaine de minutes, en remuant r\\u00e9guli\\u00e8rement, jusqu\\u2019\\u00e0 ce que les p\\u00e2tes soient al dente et la sauce bien cr\\u00e9meuse.<\\/li>\\n \\t<li style=\\\"margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; padding-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f2f6;\\\">D\\u00e9couvrir en fin de c